NextRadioTV Opposes TF1’s LCI Free Broadcast Plans, Figaro Says

-- B y   M e l i s s a   P o z s g a y
-- 
2011-07-21T06:03:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/nextradiotv-opposes-tf1-s-lci-free-broadcast-plans-figaro-says.html
NextRadioTV (NXTV)  plans to fight any
plans by rival  Societe Television Francaise 1 (TFI)  to broadcast its
24-hour news channel LCI free as part of France’s terrestrial
digital television offering, Le Figaro reported, citing
NextRadioTV Chief Executive Officer Alain Weill.  Weill also said that in the coming days NextRadioTV will
report a positive gross operating profit for the first half.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Melissa Pozsgay in Paris at 
 mpozsgay@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vidya Root at 
 vroot@bloomberg.net  